title: Quran Tafseer in Urdu - *FULL* - Dr. Israr Ahmed
description: Complete Tafseer/detailed explanation of the Quran in Urdu by the late renowned scholar Dr. Israr Ahmed.  This work of Dr. Israr is being used today by scholars such as Dr. Zakir Naik and Nouman Ali Khan.  May Allah grant Dr. Israr Ahmed a place in Janat Al-Firdous inshAllah.
